      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'This is the tutorial.

    If you step in a bushes, there''s a change
    you''ll encounter an enemy and the battle starts.

    Everytime you attack,
    you have to answer a question. If your answer is correct, the enemy gets hit.
    If your answer is wrong, you get hit.

    The battle ends when you defeat the
    enemy or when you lose your HP (Health Points).

    Good luck!

'
